Commented on #89 PHP 8.0 is not supported, PHP 8.1 is the minimum version required

Also the dev requirements do not allow to work with PHP8.0: - Root composer.json requires phpunit/phpunit ^10.0.0 -> satisfiable by phpunit/phpunit[10.0.0, ..., 10.5.46]. - phpunit/phpunit[10.0.0, ..., 10.5.46] require php >=8.1 -> your php version (8.0.30) does not satisfy that requirement. I suppose the CI tests get over this because the PHP version and matching phpunit version are explicitly specified in the matrix, therefore, the versions specified in the composer.json are ignored.
